div.div: Ise and Shima, both in their fourth year of working, are sharing a room. In order to escape their boring lives, they decide to "challenge" each other every month to do various things. One day, the challenge is to "fall in love"? Be cute! The challenge is to become a more conscious member of society! This is a comedy about living together, where every day turns into something fun little by little!
